{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b42b998035","title":"中央军委规定","origin":"根据浙江省联总《红色风暴》编辑部编印《无产阶级文化大革命文件汇编（1966.5-1968.12）》， 1968年12月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"066d05c5fc","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":8,"articleId":"b42b998035"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd2853b5ab","type":"title","text":"中央军委规定","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b42b998035"},{"id":"3084918218","type":"paragraph","text":"一，海军，空军，飞行航校，各军以下单位一律不搞四大，进行正面教育。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b42b998035"},{"id":"2f75c947c0","type":"paragraph","text":"二，海军舰队，机关和各军区，空军领导机关暂不搞四大，什么时间，另行通知。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b42b998035"},{"id":"7d019d5563","type":"paragraph","text":"望各单位遵照执行。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b42b998035"},{"id":"753cba92d5","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央军委","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b42b998035"}],"page":{"id":"3f8c7dbb99","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b42b998035","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}